Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SIGNS
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PREVIEW
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BAND PRACTICE SONG
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,INSERT SONG
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.08,0:00:04.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where will we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.72,0:00:07.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been worried about that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.03,0:00:08.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should start with Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.52,0:00:10.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.19,0:00:11.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.21,0:00:14.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who was doing the vocals at that Guerilla Live show in the cafeteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:15.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:21.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl, she's always so energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.47,0:00:23.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Teasing Hinata and laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.47,0:00:26.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She does the vocals for the band, and has ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:30.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like she's pretty fulfilled, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:32.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All she needs is a little push.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:36.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can give her that push, she can leave this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:38.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just get that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:40.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's how you feel, that's good with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.91,0:00:41.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You approve of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.08,0:00:42.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:43.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how did your task go?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.14,0:00:48.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it took some time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:51.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand Sonic: Version 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:57.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Hand Sonic: Version 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.21,0:01:01.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of an Angel... you're more like a Devil, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.43,0:01:04.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You said I'm supposed to be the coldhearted Tenshi, so make it ominous-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:06.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I did it like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:07.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No good?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:09.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.09,0:01:10.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really horrible-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:11.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Horrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.87,0:01:13.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No no, I mean it's great.  Really great!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.48,0:01:17.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and can you grow wings?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.59,0:01:18.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wings?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.07,0:01:20.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What would I do with those?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.67,0:01:23.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think they'd look cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:24.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to look cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.72,0:01:27.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you had them you'd look more like an Angel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:29.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.87,0:01:31.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:33.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, now what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.96,0:01:35.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:37.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:40.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You appear right in the middle of their band practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.90,0:01:41.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then say this:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:45.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"I've been getting complaints about noise from the other clubs."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.44,0:01:47.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then point at Yui and say...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:49.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"I think your guitar playing is horrible."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.24,0:01:52.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Because of you, the band is dying."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:55.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Therefore, I will be confiscating your guitar for a while."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:59.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, grab Yui's guitar and take your leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:02.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, Yui will give chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:03.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You just run.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:05.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, come to the courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:08.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pretend to run into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:11.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time, you drop the guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:13.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll grab it, so you take that chance to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:17.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}That'll make it so Yui and I are alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:18.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:20.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:23.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, pick a good time during their practice and {\i1}go{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:37.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:40.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:43.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't keep playing on with rhythm as bad as {\i1}that{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:44.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:49.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui... isn't it about time you concentrate on either vocals or guitar?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:51.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:52.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The way things are now, we're sounding pretty awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:53.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:56.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Iwasawa-san played and sang at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:59.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because Iwasawa was good at both.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:02.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying my best, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:05.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all just being too harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.17,0:03:07.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't everyone have a great time at our last live show?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:10.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well this time is an all-new song.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:13.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:19.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The band is dying because of your guitar playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.23,0:03:24.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She realized our band's weak point that quickly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.31,0:03:26.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not one to be trifled with!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:28.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She understands our music after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:29.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:32.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hoped everyone wouldn't pick up on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:36.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, I'll be confiscating your guitar for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:41.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:43.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:44.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:47.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:49.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't chase me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:05.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey yeah, without the guitar you don't get mixed up at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:08.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but doesn't the sound come off as weaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:10.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We need a rhythm guitar too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:12.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, should we audition for another guitarist?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:15.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm trying to say is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.10,0:04:20.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Having the vocalist also play guitar has the most impact after all, damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:21.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:23.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, Hisako-san's pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:25.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go get my guitar back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.38,0:04:25.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:28.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  Hey, Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:28.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:31.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd she go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.09,0:04:33.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, there she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:34.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:43.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:48.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stupid!  That's way too high!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My guitaaaaaaar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:57.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, it's saf{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:00.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You protected it from Tenshi, didn't you, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:03.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!  Where'd she go, damn it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:06.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, what do you mean, "damn it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:08.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing whatever you want, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:10.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Whatever I want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:12.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not doing whatever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:14.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing the band's vocals, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:15.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're even playing the guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:17.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not that big a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.55,0:05:19.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just one of the many things I've always wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:21.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  You mean there are others?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:23.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, tons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:24.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tons?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:26.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find a better place to discuss this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:32.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, like what else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I really have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:37.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to, it's alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:41.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:42.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:47.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.69,0:05:50.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got more things I want to do than most people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:51.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.19,0:05:54.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because... of {\i1}that{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:56.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't do it while you were alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:59.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.  That's it exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:04.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hit from behind by a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:05.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:08.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My body couldn't move anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:11.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was completely confined to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:15.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't live without nursing aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:18.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was completely dependent on my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:20.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:23.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd done something horrible to my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:26.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I could watch the TV, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:28.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I watched bands on music programs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:32.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought how great it would be if I could do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:37.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:38.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well good for you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:39.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:42.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what else did you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:44.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Baseball, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:45.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I watched a lot of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:48.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well if it's baseball you want, we did a lot of that at the ball game, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.23,0:06:50.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to hit at the time, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:50.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A run?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.96,0:06:52.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A home run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:52.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:54.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good without one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:56.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No good at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:07:02.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If things start going better with the band, I was thinking that I'd start practicing my baseball skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:05.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is gonna be harder than I thought.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:07.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's hear the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:08.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:08.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Soccer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:09.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Soccer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:11.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was pretty big, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:13.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... yeah, I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:15.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's got way too many interests!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:19.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where in the world would you find someone who's in a band, plays baseball,{\i0} and {\i1}plays soccer?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:21.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely, there's not any others, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:22.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pro Wrestling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:25.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't get it.  Where in the world would you find someone who...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:29.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait a minute... she only wants to do stuff she saw on TV.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:32.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But this is tough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:34.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Trying to make all of that come true...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:38.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:41.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it all come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.05,0:07:43.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First up is, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:45.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The easy stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:47.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do some Pro Wrestling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:48.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!  Pro Wrestling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:49.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your special move?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:51.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,German Suplex!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:53.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can do a move like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:56.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you pick a hold, or something that seems remotely possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:08:00.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've always admired it.  The German Suplex.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.34,0:08:02.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Winning a match with that hold...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.74,0:08:04.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such violent stuff so cutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:09.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gahhhhh... okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:11.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, let's try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:12.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:13.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:18.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.67,0:08:22.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're stronger than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:23.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:32.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's too much for a girl like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:33.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, you almost did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:35.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were super-close!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:36.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:38.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I try one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:43.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... for now, can we go somewhere with softer ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:44.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:46.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:48.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that wasn't a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:52.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Orya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:53.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:56.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry!  I'll do it right next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:58.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is seriously the last time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:09:00.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oraaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.42,0:09:01.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:03.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpaiiiiii!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:07.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, can you even do a bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.22,0:09:08.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:09.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:16.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So{\i0} this {\i1}was the problem.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:19.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because of this, I almost lost consciousness how many times?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:22.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to train you to do a bridge first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:24.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, that's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:25.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:27.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:30.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.  You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:33.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, that's no good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:36.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never done anything like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:39.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't do this, you'll never do a German Suplex.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:41.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:48.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're shaking quite a bit, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.53,0:09:51.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:55.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.  Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:56.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.92,0:10:03.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoa.  Her hands are wrapped completely around my stomach!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:05.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't escape!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:06.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is perfect.  It's perfect!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:10.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a German Suplex!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:13.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,1...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:14.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,2...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,3...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:17.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ding ding ding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Match over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:21.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:26.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.11,0:10:28.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:32.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I did it!  I did it!  Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.43,0:10:31.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How much longer do I have to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:35.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:50.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we go for soccer next?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:52.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A 1-on-1 penalty kick works, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:53.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:56.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta take out 5 guys with my dribbling skills and then score.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:10:59.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Maradona.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:01.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:03.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:04.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.21,0:11:09.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, TK.  You know where Matsushita-godan is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:10.95,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,The way he is now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:13.05,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't dance in my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:14.79,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let me cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:16.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:17.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:18.51,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Training in seclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:19.60,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,In the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:21.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mountain training?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:24.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the last place I'd think of dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:27.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, he won't be back for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.29,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Woooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:32.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, fine.  You'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:35.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you help me get 4 players?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:38.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm keeping it a secret from Yuri, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:41.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got this letter from Tenshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:44.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you can't compete with one little girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:47.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,hearing you call yourselves men is preposterous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:50.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.  "Preposterous", I'm surprised you could read that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:51.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Has your stupidity been cured?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:53.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Naw, even idiots can read.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:59.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat the girliness out of you with sportsmanship?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:02.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting on the soccer field after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:03.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:04.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.36,0:12:07.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.73,0:12:09.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she really write that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:12.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The current Tenshi is different from the old one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:17.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's all mixed up inside her, so this idiotic letter of challenge is the best she could do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:20.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I can play along with something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:22.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm reporting this to Yurippe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:24.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I already said we need to keep this secret from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:25.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:29.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we tell Yuri, it'll turn into another armed conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:32.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it says we'll settle this with sportsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:35.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's saying we'll settle things fair and square through sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:39.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, it's addressed to the men.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.26,0:12:42.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we go and tattle to Yuri, that'll make us look even less manly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:48.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, should we go with us 5 then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:49.45,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:50.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:52.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:53.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:55.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:56.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:01.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:02.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:03.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you came?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kickoff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:07.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She started kicking the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:09.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:11.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it!  The one who wrote that letter was her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:15.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be fed up with us being such wimps.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:16.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she's doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:18.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!  Let's protect the goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:19.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't lose this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:21.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We men will {\i1}win{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:25.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:26.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:28.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:29.16,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,I kiss you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:30.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata!  You're the Goalkeeper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:31.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:33.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the way, fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:36.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.  What lousy dribbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:37.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wide open!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.91,0:13:39.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:42.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!  One down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:45.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:47.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Noda?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:49.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 2!  Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:53.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ref!  That was a red card just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.09,0:13:54.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:56.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:58.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still coming, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:14:00.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, TK, Otonashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:01.94,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy come, easy go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:02.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:04.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:07.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.78,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Woo! Here we go{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:09.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:11.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, whose side are you on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:17.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The last one is... you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:20.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll steal this goal if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:22.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd your "sportsmanship" go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:24.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.74,0:14:25.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.56,0:14:28.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure Kill Guillotine Murder Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:33.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she want to get a goal or kill me?\NThere's too many jokes to be made here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:35.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!  It's a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinataaaaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:44.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:46.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It... went in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:48.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:50.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it, I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:51.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won against 5 people!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.69,0:14:51.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:54.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We... lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:56.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Against Yui all by herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:58.74,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Scrambled it, trouble down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:00.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:02.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep this a secret for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:03.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:08.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, she got the ball taken once, and she didn't really get past the goalkeeper, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:09.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good enough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:18.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:21.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's do the next one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:25.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we start, how far does it have to go to count as a home run?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:28.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Past the fence, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.31,0:15:31.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:35.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well alright, just hit it as hard as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:41.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to do more than just hit it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:43.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the ball more carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:44.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit it with the center of the bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:48.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hitting it from too high up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:53.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That time was too low!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:57.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't hit it with your eyes shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:04.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No power...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:06.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, try!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:08.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:10.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:12.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:15.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too tired.  Your grip is weakening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:17.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in continuing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.90,0:16:20.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1700)}Awwww!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:37.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your shouts are getting louder, but your hits aren't going any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:39.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.59,0:16:42.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}Aww, close...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:48.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:52.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dark to see the ball anymore today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:56.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Awwww.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:13.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:19.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna play, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:20.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Some real baseball?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:21.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Full swing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.51,0:17:24.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't done one in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:27.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:28.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,... is nice once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:42.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.53,0:17:44.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're barely swinging at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:56.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:58.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme see your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:17:59.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:00.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:05.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not surprising.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:07.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was impossible from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:10.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm giving up on this dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:11.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:12.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:15.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you do all this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:16.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:18.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,... what you wanted to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to keep going 'til the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:24.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreaming of hitting a home run is more like a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:29.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I couldn't hit a home run, I was able to move my body so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:31.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:34.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Every day was like being in a club.  It was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:37.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:39.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't move my body before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:41.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So this was a ton of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:47.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, they've all come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:48.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:49.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What has?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:53.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... the things you wanted to do when you couldn't move your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:55.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:57.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've still got one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:18:57.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:18:59.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.81,0:19:02.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The ultimate happiness for a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:05.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:07.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't clean or do laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:10.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even that.  I can't do anything alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.20,0:19:11.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I cause nothing but trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:12.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:15.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would want to marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:19.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,God sure is cruel, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:21.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had all my happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:24.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,... taken away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:27.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not... true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:32.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.38,0:19:37.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:50.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:54.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:58.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... dead serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:01.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:05.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even know the real me, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:09.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care how you were in reality, when you were alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:11.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll marry you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:14.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what handicaps you may have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:16.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:17.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:19.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I said no matter what handicaps you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:22.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can't walk or stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:24.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can't have children.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:28.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I'll marry you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:33.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:37.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Yui I met here, she's not just a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.74,0:20:38.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:41.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where we meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:44.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have still fallen for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:48.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If by a one-in-a-million chance we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:53.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're in a body that won't move again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:56.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.53,0:20:59.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.37,0:21:02.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui... she'll be stuck at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:05.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... play baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:10.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, {\i1}bam{\i0}, I'll break the window of your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:13.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I go to find the ball, you'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:16.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how we'll meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.58,0:21:21.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After we get to talking, we'll get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.62,0:21:23.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start going to your house every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.98,0:21:25.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start learning to care for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:26.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How does that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:28.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:33.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, when that time comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.19,0:21:36.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who always cared for me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:38.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who tried so hard for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:40.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.93,0:21:42.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of her too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:44.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.39,0:21:49.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1100)}I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.96,0:22:49.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.02,0:22:53.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.59,0:22:58.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.73,0:23:01.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stick around 'til the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.59,0:23:05.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still plenty of people for me to worry about here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.49,0:23:07.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.48,0:23:54.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did I just cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.89,0:23:57.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.74,0:24:00.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to clarify that a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.19,0:24:02.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't explain any better than to say it was a shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.58,0:24:05.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda just rushed here and defeated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.85,0:24:08.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Ooyama-san had been left alone, it would've been dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.18,0:24:10.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.42,0:24:12.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it?
