Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.21,0:24:20.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c170] I wanted to help too! {Boku mo tasukeyou to shitanda!}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.04,0:24:21.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c141] I don't need reinforcements! {Kasei nado iran!}
