Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.15,0:24:24.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c211] Isn't being erased by Tenshi even better? {Tenshi ni kesarechimatta hou ga mashi janee ka yo?}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.98,0:24:23.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c192] Gonna disappear! {Kieru zo!}
