Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:05.60,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(440,480)}Every time we met up
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:10.35,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(440,260)}the two of us would always fight
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:16.63,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(230,480)}But that's still a wonderful memory to me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:25.42,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(440,0)}You taught me that there's nothing to be afraid of
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.42,0:20:29.22,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how physically impaired I may be
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:33.41,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,I can still hold onto happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:37.38,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,330)}So that's why
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:45.42,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(440,300)}I'll continue on alone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.42,0:20:49.31,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it might be painful
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:57.42,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,320)}I'll definitely bring with me the dream we saw together
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:01.08,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:05.39,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,Not with anybody else
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:09.16,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was no good after all
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:13.86,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,540)}You're not here after all
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:33.74,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(540,480)}I always felt like
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:38.23,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(440,430)}You were only humoring me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:41.90,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(440,0)}But it was just a feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:44.65,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,650)}Please understand that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.85,0:21:53.40,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(540,0)}I don't regret being born anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.40,0:21:57.36,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the end of a carnival
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.36,0:22:06.17,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,850)}It's a little sad, but it's time to go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.96,0:22:13.42,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(440,280)}I'll go any distance
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.42,0:22:17.18,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,340)}With the things I learned here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.18,0:22:25.36,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,0)}The dream called happiness, I'll grant it for sure
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.36,0:22:33.38,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm seperated from you, no matter how far away you are
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.38,0:22:41.28,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,190)}I'll be living in a new morning
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.28,0:22:45.11,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,As things shift and change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.11,0:22:49.33,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(270,240)}And time begins to fade
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:53.11,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened before
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.11,0:22:57.04,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:23:01.02,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.02,0:23:05.32,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}I can hear someone softly laughing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:09.10,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason right now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.10,0:23:13.39,Insert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,840)}That's my greatest treasure in the world
